{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Concept</h2>Little Legend is like a Metroidvania but in an open world with lots of loots and secrets. Many quests awaits you, but you're free to explore at yout own pace. By day, by night, on land or in the air!<br><br>A deep battle system based on spells chaining.<br>Summon Sphere, cast Force Push and you get a blunt projectile. Useful to hurt an enemy, destroy a fragile wall or solve a puzzle. Spells are as effective for fighting as for exploring.<br><br>The night is coming and it's time to take a break in the Haven. Craft potions to recover or handcrafted jewels for money. Improve yout stats and get new skills by resurrecting a guardian.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Create your own Magic Spells &amp; Guardians<br></li><li>Explore freely and achieve quests in a beautiful 2D open world<br></li><li>Fight with tool-like spells and create unexpected effects<br></li><li>Improve your spells, stats and get new skills from guardians<br></li><li>Craft items with engaging and deep mechanics<br></li><li>Talk with animals, swim and fly by turning yourself into a weasel<br></li><li>Earn money by finding a job or by selling your crafted works.<br></li><li>Discover a 5-year character-driven story about resilience<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987310/extras/banner_throne_b.png?t=1693231768\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987310/extras/addtowishlist.gif?t=1693231768\" /></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987310/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1693231768","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987310/page.bg.jpg?t=1693231768","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987310/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1693231768","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987310/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1693231768","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>JOIN THE COMMUNITY</h1><p>Join our community on Discord and help us shape Little Legend :)<br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Concept</h2>Little Legend is like a Metroidvania but in an open world with lots of loots and secrets. Many quests awaits you, but you're free to explore at yout own pace. By day, by night, on land or in the air!<br><br>A deep battle system based on spells chaining.<br>Summon Sphere, cast Force Push and you get a blunt projectile. Useful to hurt an enemy, destroy a fragile wall or solve a puzzle. Spells are as effective for fighting as for exploring.<br><br>The night is coming and it's time to take a break in the Haven. Craft potions to recover or handcrafted jewels for money. Improve yout stats and get new skills by resurrecting a guardian.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Create your own Magic Spells &amp; Guardians<br></li><li>Explore freely and achieve quests in a beautiful 2D open world<br></li><li>Fight with tool-like spells and create unexpected effects<br></li><li>Improve your spells, stats and get new skills from guardians<br></li><li>Craft items with engaging and deep mechanics<br></li><li>Talk with animals, swim and fly by turning yourself into a weasel<br></li><li>Earn money by finding a job or by selling your crafted works.<br></li><li>Discover a 5-year character-driven story about resilience<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987310/extras/banner_throne_b.png?t=1693231768\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987310/extras/addtowi